title: Time required to start a business, male (days)
name: ic.reg.durs.ma
readme: Time required to start a business is the number of calendar days needed to complete the procedures to legally operate a business. If a procedure can be speeded up at additional cost, the fastest procedure, independent of cost, is chosen.
